ight better explain differences among species in arabinose absorption.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Price, Edwin R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rott, Katherine H.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Caviedes-Vidal, Enrique", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Karasov, William H.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Animals", "Arvicolinae", "Chiroptera", "Claudins", "Comparative transcriptomics", "Gene Expression Regulation", "Hedgehogs", "Intestinal Absorption", "Intestinal Mucosa", "Intestine", "Intestines", "Occludin", "Paracellular absorption", "Species Specificity", "Tight junction", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/4e0234e86aa566a11b80819ee915c508", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/0c6b525886a9847ea761fe03312b4912f4cb7368e4c4bb566fe85db72f1fdd16", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/99EFETH9", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/99EFETH9", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/e9b08c1875d15148e2475848d0adb850!/b307270-310277", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "36-45", "title": "Comparative Biochemistry and Physiology. Part B, Biochemistry & Molecular Biology", "volume": "191"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/4e0234e86aa566a11